data.description: Exceptional, all-brick colonial on 1+ acre lot.  This immaculately maintained home has many special features with more than 5,000 sq ft of living space.  The main level has a welcoming entry,  open concept family room off the updated kitchen, den/office, sunroom, living and dining rooms.  The family room has a cozy fireplace and is perfectly situated for entertaining, with easy access to kitchen and deck.  The upper level has 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 remodeled bathrooms and large laundry room.  The lower level has something for everyone with a rec room, family room with fireplace, full bath, 5th bedroom, den, lots of storage and walkout to patio.  The exterior will wow you with a large deck and amazing, level backyard perfect for entertaining and gaming.  This home has new windows, newer roof,  brand new HVAC, tankless water heater and newer septic system.  Conveniently located in quiet neighborhood just 5 minutes to Old Town Warrenton and comes with high speed internet!
